title: Convenient Single family home near Santa Clara Square
posting_body: ['Two storey 1600 sq ft single family home in a convenient location near hi-tech companies (Santa Clara Square).', 'Key features:', '- New Agnew School District schools (Middle: Dolores Huerta; High: Kathleen MacDonald)', '- Easy access to Santa Clara Square, 49er Levi stadium, Great America, Rivermark plaza, light rail, ACE train station', '- Easy commute on 101, 237, 880, 87 -- against traffic', '- Open floor plan', '- Central heating and the A/C', '- Stainless steel appliances', '- Quartz countertop', '- Master bedroom with walk-in closet with spacious built in shelves', '- Jack and Jill guest bathroom', '- Easy to maintain backyard with beautiful rose bushes', '- Attached spacious 2 car garage', '- Good credit and proof of income required', '- Contact via email for appointments to view', '- Terms negotiable; longer lease is also possible']
